BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thrikketta-20260628@openai
DTSTAMP:20260626T065109Z
DTSTART;TZID=Asia/Dubai:20260628T060000
DTEND;TZID=Asia/Dubai:20260628T070000
SUMMARY:Thrikketta Nakshatra Remedies
DESCRIPTION:Thrikketta Nakshatra remedies from astrologer:\n\nVishnu/Krishna temple:\n- Offer paal-payasam (milk kheer).\n- Light ghee lamp (neyy-vilakku).\n- Offer tulsi garland (tulasi mala).\n\nSerpent shrine (Sarpa kavu / Naga temple):\n- Do noorum-palum: turmeric + milk offering to Naga deities.\n\nBhadrakali temple:\n- Raktha pushpaanjali with red flowers.\n- Offer kadum-payasam (jaggery-based sweet).\n\nNote: Nakshatra timings can vary by location and panchangam. Verify exact start/end time with a local Malayalam calendar if timing is important.
CATEGORIES:Thrikketta,Nakshatra,Malayalam Calendar
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Thrikketta tomorrow - prepare offerings/remedies.
TRIGGER:-P1D
END:VALARM
